Package: VolatilityDashboard
Type: Package
Title: Volatility Modeling Dashboard for Financial Time Series
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: person("BenoÃ®t", "Mayer", email = "mayer.benoit@gmail.com",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: An interactive Shiny dashboard for volatility modeling and forecasting.
    Supports multiple model families including GARCH, EWMA, MA, and machine learning models.
    Integrates Yahoo Finance data and Deribit BTC options data. Provides comprehensive
    statistical analysis, model comparison with Diebold-Mariano tests, and interactive
    visualizations using Plotly.
